<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-787] Fault mediator creates an invalid SOAP 1.2 SOAP fault</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-787</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Following configuration segment&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;            &amp;lt;property name=&quot;ERROR_CODE&quot; value=&quot;Receiver&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;property name=&quot;ERROR_MESSAGE&quot; value=&quot;systemError&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;makefault version=&quot;soap12&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;code expression=&quot;get-property(&apos;ERROR_CODE&apos;)&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;reason expression=&quot;get-property(&apos;ERROR_MESSAGE&apos;)&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;detail expression=&quot;get-property(&apos;ERROR_DETAIL&apos;)&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/makefault&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;creates a following SOAP fault&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2003/05/soap-envelope&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;soapenv:Body&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;soapenv:Fault&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;soapenv:Code&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;soapenv:Value&amp;gt;axis2ns7:Receiver&amp;lt;/soapenv:Value&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/soapenv:Code&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;soapenv:Reason&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;soapenv:Text&amp;gt;customerNotExist&amp;lt;/soapenv:Text&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/soapenv:Reason&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;soapenv:Detail&amp;gt;System out of resources&amp;lt;/soapenv:Detail&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/soapenv:Fault&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/soapenv:Body&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/soapenv:Envelope&amp;gt; &lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;which has 2 errors.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;axis2ns7 is not defined&lt;br/&gt;
soapenv:Text element does not has mandatory lang attribute &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/soap12-part1/#reasontextelement&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.w3.org/TR/soap12-part1/#reasontextelement&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
